response.summary:
I have more than 4 years of experience working with big data and various artificial intelligence applications, such as NLP, machine vision, and most recently, working with GPT-3 for AI models. Since finishing my bachelor's degree, I started working with financial data and contributed to the production of several academic articles related to financial data analysis by training predictive models for the financial market. Machine learning and big data techniques were used to train automatic trading models for these articles.
I was part of the winning team at the artificial intelligence Hackathon at the AI LATIN AMERICA SUMMIT event at the Massachusetts Institute of Technology. Additionally, I was part of ALGOS Trade, a research group from the National University of Colombia that studies various machine learning techniques applied to finance.
Currently, I am working on developing artificial intelligence models for implementation in mixed reality devices. My experience includes programming scalable applications on the Google Cloud Platform (GCP).
